cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CC

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it presents a dataset for evaluating the grammaticality of language models. It may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it discusses the performance of an LSTM language model and the potential for improvement in capturing syntax. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks, and cs.CC (Computational Complexity) as it evaluates the complexity of language models in capturing syntax.
